2005;;Brothers of the Head;;British;;Keith Fulton, Louis Pepe;;Harry Treadaway, Luke Treadaway;;mockumentary;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brothers_of_the_Head;;In the early 1970s, the twins are essentially purchased by sleazy talent manager with plans to turn them into rock stars. The brothers form a punk rock band called the Bang Bang. As the band's success grows, a music journalist, Laura (Tania Emery), follows the band writing an article. A romantic relationship develops between Laura and Tom causing friction between the two brothers.